  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: It's time for you to make an important decision.
    nextOption: Really? What's that?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Before beginning training, you must choose your path.
    nextOption: Which path?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'All SunSworn must devote themselves to a training path.


      In
      order to be effective, you must concentrate on a set of related skills.  This
      will help you learn faster.


      Which path would you like to follow?'
    nextOption: What are my options?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'I can guide you through that choice.


      Talk to me again to
      get details about all of the available paths.


      Then choose the one that
      sounds best.  You can always change your mind later.'
    nextOption: Great, tell me my options
